fields.notes:
- From beginning of f2 coverage to 1996-01-01, we have only precedential cases (f2 and f3).
 - From 1996-01-01 to 2007-07-31 we have f3 cases and scraped non-precedential ones. Merging the scraped precedential cases with the f3 corpus was too difficult and provided no new opinions. Unfortunately, it appears that we have a lot of duplicates from f3 and scraping in 1996. This can be seen as a bump in the coverage page.
 - From 2007-08-01 onwards, we have scraped cases.
